700757f-a.folder: City Island Avenue & Centre Street, Bronx, NY
700757f-a.original_title: Bronx: City Island Avenue - Centre Street
700757f-a.text:
City Island Ave. (City Island), south from Centre Street. On the west side of the street appears the yard of Henry B. Nevins Inc., yacht builder.
July 6, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
